Define sets A and B as follow://定义集合A和B如下所示
A = {m∈Z | m = 6r + 12 for some r∈Z}
B = {n∈Z | n = 3s for some s∈Z}
a.Outline a proof that A B. b.Prove that A B c.Disprove that B A.
